snippet.title: TEKKEN 8 — Lidia Sobieska Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Let's make this fight one to be proud of. Lidia Sobieska, The Warrior Prime Minister, enters King of Iron Fist Tournament on July 25th in PDT with early access on July 22nd in PDT for Playable Character Year 1 Pass holders.

Join the official TEKKEN Discord server 👉 https://bnent.eu/TekkenDiscord
